    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to show you this absolute gem! Honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible shape, it still feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, and it\u2019s completely spotless inside and out\u2014not a single scratch or scuff to be found. It drives like a dream and is ready for its next adventure. You\u2019ve really got to see it in person to believe how gorgeous it is! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
