      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offering a truly collector-grade vehicle that presents in showroom condition. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage and has never seen inclement weather. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory-original luster with no swirl marks, stone chips, or door dings, and has been protected with a professional ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is immaculate; the premium leather seats show zero bolster wear, the carpets are pristine, and it still retains that 'new car' scent. Every electronic feature, from the infotainment system to the heated seat elements, functions perfectly. Mechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach, featuring a fully documented service history with all maintenance performed ahead of schedule by certified technicians. All original keys, owner\u2019s manuals, and a thick folder of service receipts are included. This is a rare opportunity to own a flawless, turn-key example for the discerning enthusiast.",
